# DAY 26 PHASE 2B: Selected Branch Execution Steering Pack
# Transitions from shadow motor imagery to gated overt software action initiation.
# Selected futures partially bias real edit intent generation under rollback-first
# safety constraints. Repeated successes consolidate into strategic software habits.
# Waking-only. Zero survival contamination. Biology zero-bias law preserved.
