# DAY 26 PHASE 2B: Strategic Subgoal Execution Pack
# Extends habit-conditioned action bias into multi-step software execution
# sequences. Policy priors shape bounded subgoal chains. Delayed credit
# assignment over temporal horizons, analogous to cortical sequence planning
# and reinforcement consolidation in prefrontal-basal-ganglia circuits.
# Waking-only. Zero survival contamination. Biology exclusion law preserved.
