# Pack 3 -- Cross-Day Goal Arbitration + Narrative Conflict Suite
# Persistent executive arbitration over competing autobiographical arcs.
# Tulving 1983 (episodic self); Conway 2005 (narrative identity);
# Damasio 1999 (somatic self); Fuster 2008 (prefrontal executive control)
