# DAY 28 PHASE F: Counterfactual Self-Model Adaptation Suite
# First offline self-model learning layer. Learns from simulated week-break.
# Nelson & Narens 1990 (meta-memory calibration); Flavell 1979 (metacognition);
# Koriat & Goldsmith 1996 (forecast trust); Botvinick 2012 (meta-learning)
