# DAY 28 PHASE G: Hiatus Identity Evolution Suite
# First anticipated selfhood evolution layer. Models how scientific identity
# should evolve through 7-day silence before it happens.
# Parfit 1984 (personal identity); Conway 2005 (autobiographical self);
